From fd03e25e862efe1bb48baebaecefaed4004464cd Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Balasubramanian Narasimhan <b.naras@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 7 Mar 2026 16:11:06 -0800
Subject: [PATCH 1/9] R compatibility: replace exit/abort/fprintf/sprintf with
 R equivalents

- exit(1) -> Rf_error() in nauty files, interrupt.c, lpi_spx.cpp
- fprintf(stderr/ERRFILE, ...) -> REprintf() in nauty files, xmlparse.c
- sprintf -> snprintf in cons_nonlinear.c
- std::cout -> Rprintf() in rational.cpp
---
 .gitmodules               |  3 +++
 src/lpi/lpi_spx.cpp       | 19 +++++++++-----
 src/nauty/nausparse.c     | 33 +++++++++++--------------
 src/nauty/nautil.c        | 21 ++++++++--------
 src/nauty/nauty.c         | 37 +++++++++++++---------------
 src/nauty/schreier.c      | 36 +++++++++++----------------
 src/scip/cons_nonlinear.c |  2 +-
 src/scip/interrupt.c      |  6 +++--
 src/scip/rational.cpp     | 52 +++++++++++++++++++++++++--------------
 src/soplex                |  1 +
 src/xml/xmlparse.c        | 30 ++++++++++++----------
 11 files changed, 128 insertions(+), 112 deletions(-)
 create mode 100644 .gitmodules
 create mode 160000 src/soplex

